Sentencas: Composites consisting of Ag-Y025Bi0.75O1.5 (YSB) were investigated as composite cathodes for intermediate-solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Fabrication of thin Ag-YSB composite cathode film for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: A thin film of Ag-YSB composite cathode was fabricated by using slurry painting method.
Titulo: Fabrication of thin Ag-YSB composite cathode film for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The slurry of Ag-YSB composite cathodes was used to coat anode-bilayered electrolytes (NiOSDC/SDC/YSB) at room temperature.
Titulo: Fabrication of thin Ag-YSB composite cathode film for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: TGA and DSC results confirmed that all the organic components in the slurry were completely decomposed at temperatures below 600 degrees C. XRD analysis revealed the formation of a pure Ag-YSB composite cathode phase.
Titulo: Fabrication of thin Ag-YSB composite cathode film for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: SEM images showed the grain size increment of the AgYSB powder that was ascribed to the consolidation between adjacent grains, which reduced the size of the porosity as the heat treatment temperature was increased.
Titulo: Fabrication of thin Ag-YSB composite cathode film for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The electrochemical performances (interfacial polarization resistance, R-p) were 0.483, 0.469, 0.416, and 0.441 Omega cm(2) after one, two, three, and four coatings, respectively.
Titulo: Fabrication of thin Ag-YSB composite cathode film for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells
